Task 2: Simple Digit Calculator

This task involves designing a clean and interactive calculator web application.
It supports basic arithmetic operations like addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division.
The interface is user-friendly with well-spaced buttons and a clear display area.
Keyboard input support improves usability and makes calculations faster.
This task demonstrates logical implementation, UI design, and basic TypeScript usage.

GitHub Repository Link:
https://github.com/Lavanya11-blip/simple-digit

